**4.3 POME Iron (Fe) --- Inclusion Rate Logic**

Heavy metals of concern: Fe (3,000--8,000 mg/kg DM) and Mn (100--475
mg/kg DM). Fe result drives POME sludge inclusion rate in substrate
blend:

  ----------------- ----------------- -----------------------------------
  **Fe Level (mg/kg **POME Inclusion  **Action**
  DM)**             (WW %)**          

  \< 3,000          **Up to 20%**     Standard inclusion

  3,000 -- 5,000    **10--15%**       Reduced inclusion

  5,000 -- 8,000    **5--10%**        Minimal inclusion; CaCO₃ amendment

  \> 8,000          **CaCO₃ amendment CaCO₃ added to chelate excess iron
                    required**        
  ----------------- ----------------- -----------------------------------

