**10.2 Equipment Derating**

Asian/China equipment derated at 65% of nameplate capacity by default
across all models. This is applied in all mass balance calculations.

**11. Nutrient Ledger & Soil Calculator**

The Nutrient Ledger is a persistent panel displayed at the end of every
stage tab in the React dashboard. It shows nutrient flow through the
pipeline at each stage, enabling the estate agronomist to see the NPK
value building across the process.

**11.1 Nutrient Ledger Panel --- Required Fields**

  ----------------------- ----------------------- -----------------------
  **Field**               **Unit 1**              **Unit 2**

  Nitrogen (N)            \% DM                   kg/day

  Phosphorus (P)          \% DM                   kg/day

  Potassium (K)           \% DM                   kg/day

  Calcium (Ca)            \% DM                   kg/day

  Magnesium (Mg)          \% DM                   kg/day

  Organic Matter (OM)     \% DM                   kg/day

  Soil-adjusted effective By soil type (VGAM      USD/t FW
  value                   tier)                   

  NPK replacement cost    USD/day                 USD/tonne
  ----------------------- ----------------------- -----------------------

**11.2 Soil Calculator**

The Soil Calculator (CFI_Soil_Calculator_v4_PUBLISHED.jsx) allows the
estate agronomist to calculate site-specific fertiliser replacement
value based on soil type, management tier, and product blend. It uses
the five Indonesian soil profiles and the VGAM/GAM/Poor/Abandoned
management tiers. Peak fertiliser cost at Year 7--15:
\$10--\$16/palm/yr.

