  **Colour**              **Use**

  Amber text on navy      **User-editable input fields**
  background              

  Green text              **Calculated output values**

  Teal                    **Cross-sheet / cross-tab references**

  Red                     **Guardrail alerts / hard gates / blocked
                          values**

  Navy background         Primary background for all stage panels
  (#0B1929)               
  ----------------------- -----------------------------------------------

**12.3 React Technical Rules**

-   No template literals in JSX text nodes

-   No self-closing divs

-   All \< in JSX text use entity encoding or JS expressions

-   No raw \${} in JSX text nodes --- use JS expressions

-   Babel-strict compliance --- all syntax must be Babel-parseable

-   Tailwind core utility classes only --- no compiled Tailwind

-   State management: useState, useReducer (no
    localStorage/sessionStorage)

-   All C:N ratios formula-driven --- never hardcoded

-   PKSA cost always \$0 in UI --- commercial override only in Admin
    Panel

