Six interconnected Excel workbooks cover detailed financial and process
modelling. Each workbook is built with Python/openpyxl following the
MASTER_INPUTS-first architecture. All workbooks share a single source of
truth via cross-workbook links.

  -------------- ----------- ------------ ---------- ---------------------------------
