                                                     INPUTS_S2, CHEMICAL_LIBRARY,
                                                     MASS_BALANCE, CHEMICAL_COSTS,
                                                     EQUIPMENT, S2_OPEX, S2_COSTS,
                                                     CONFLICT_CHECK, RECALC_CHECK

  **WB4**        S3          Planned      ---        Biological library; inoculation
                                                     timeline; S3 costs

  **WB5**        S4          **✅         10         Dual-track Bay A/B grow-out; PKM
                             Complete**              supplementation; mass balance;
                                                     CAPEX/OPEX

  **WB6**        S5/S6       **✅         10         Frass NPK replacement value;
