                                                     model; VGAM; carbon credits
  -------------- ----------- ------------ ---------- ---------------------------------

**13.1 Workbook Architecture Rules**

-   All workbooks use Python/openpyxl for creation and editing

-   recalc.py must run post-save --- zero formula errors on recalc is
    the completion standard

-   All C:N ratios are formula-driven --- never hardcoded in any
    workbook

-   Data-only=True when reading cell values for mass balance
    verification

-   merge_cells() must be called before writing to merged ranges

-   Cross-workbook links use teal colour convention

-   WB3 (S2) is fully specified and ready to build --- 11-tab structure
    confirmed

